<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Syzkaller on apowerfulmei</title><link>https://apowerfulmei.github.io/tags/syzkaller/</link><description>Recent content in Syzkaller on apowerfulmei</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 29 May 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://apowerfulmei.github.io/tags/syzkaller/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Syz-repro</title><link>https://apowerfulmei.github.io/p/syz-repro/</link><pubDate>Thu, 29 May 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://apowerfulmei.github.io/p/syz-repro/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="syz-repro分析">Syz-Repro分析
&lt;/h1>&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/google/syzkaller/blob/master/tools/syz-repro/repro.go" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>syzkaller/tools/syz-repro/repro.go at master · google/syzkaller&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="syz-repro的使用">syz-repro的使用
&lt;/h2>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">./bin/syz-repro -config=my.cfg /path/to/crash/log
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>使用syz-repro对log中包含的prog进行复现，这个流程包括&lt;/p>
&lt;p>1、提取出可以触发crash的初始prog&lt;/p>
&lt;p>2、对这个prog进行简化，基本采用的是逐个syscall削减简化&lt;/p>
&lt;p>3、对prog的参数等进行简化&lt;/p>
&lt;p>4、将prog转化为C poc&lt;/p>
&lt;p>5、对C poc进行简化&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="程序最小化">程序最小化
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>pkg/repro/repro.go Run runInner reproCtx.run()&lt;/p>
