&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="c1">// We do want to keep at least one call, otherwise tools/syz-execprog
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c1">// will immediately exit.
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">false&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">ret&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">err&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">:=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">ctx&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">testProg&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">p1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">res&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">Duration&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">res&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">Opts&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">false&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">if&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">err&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">!=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">nil&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nx">ctx&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">reproLogf&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mi">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;minimization failed with %v&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">err&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kc">false&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">ret&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nx">Crashed&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">})&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="k">return&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">res&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nx">nil&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>这里会调用prog中的Minimize函数对程序进行简化&lt;/p>
&lt;p>包含的参数：&lt;/p>
&lt;p>1、prog 程序列表&lt;/p>
&lt;p>2、index 开始简化的syscall下标&lt;/p>
&lt;p>3、mode 简化模式&lt;/p>
&lt;p>4、pred 测试函数，这个函数会对简化后的程序进行测试，观察其能否触发Bug&lt;/p>
